description: Ruslan Peterko and Jason Sanchez attend to the tedious process offertilizing conifers one by one. Their minds wander and soon theyfind themselves tending another type of wood...their stiff cocks.Fellow forester Robert Petri sees their stiff branches and decides torelease his own pent up wood. He pounds Jason's hole while the boydeep throats Ruslan's pole. The men feed the fire of their desire untilone by one they unleash their loads...giving the forest another kind ofnutriment.
title: Hard Wood, Scene #02
